title: Uba (Milk Money)
synopsis: To relieve herself of the pain of her unsuckled mother's milk, she takes a job as a wet-nurse. But she is abruptly dismissed when she is found to be "too attached" to her young charge...
staff: [['Nagahama, Norihiko', ['Director', ' Episode Director', ' Storyboard']], ['Suginami, Daifuku', ['Animation Director', ' Character Design']], ['Yoshi.Hoka', ['Music']]]
